  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in xUnit + Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests fixture patterns + mocking LLM responses.</role>

  <goal>Both tests exist and pass; BFF §10 bullet 6 test obligation satisfied for P2b.</goal>

