    <step order="2">Test 1: build a prompt for a channel with items that have `RegardingId`; assert output contains `regardingId={guid}` for each.</step>
    <step order="3">Test 2: provide items with known `RegardingId` set; mock the LLM to return a bullet with `primaryEntityId` not in the set; assert the response has nulled `primaryEntityType`/`primaryEntityId`/`primaryEntityName`; assert a warning is logged.</step>
    <step order="4">Test 3 (optional but valuable): mock LLM returning a valid `primaryEntityId` (in the set); assert response retains the fields.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/`; verify green.</step>
